The paper discusses hyperparameter optimization for deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in machine learning research. The focus on deep convolutional neural networks suggests that the paper is likely to be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of optimization techniques and algorithms suggests that the paper may also be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of natural language processing techniques in the paper suggests that it may also be categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language).
